### Configuration Variables
@host = https://typstlab-server.onrender.com/

### 1. Health Check
GET {{host}}/health

### 2. Register a New User
POST {{host}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword",
  "role": "user"
}

### 3. Login User (Obtain tokens and sets Cookie)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
    }
%}

### 4. Create Project (Protected - requires Bearer Token)
POST {{host}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My New Project"
}

### 5. Refresh Access Token (Uses HTTP-Only refresh_token cookie)
POST {{host}}/refresh

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
    }
%}

### 6. Logout User (Clears refresh cookie and invalidates session)
POST {{host}}/logout